#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator_uk.html:292
msgid "This calculator estimates principal and interest only."
msgstr "Dieser Rechner schätzt nur Kapital und Zinsen."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator_uk.html:293
msgid ""
"UK lender fees, insurance, and taxes are not included unless you add them "
"separately."
msgstr ""
"Gebühren, Versicherungen und Steuern des britischen Kreditgebers sind nicht "
"enthalten, es sei denn, Sie fügen sie separat hinzu."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator_uk.html:294
msgid ""
"For interest-only mortgages, the schedule shows interest payments and the "
"balance remains the same."
msgstr ""
"Bei zinslosen Hypotheken zeigt der Zeitplan die Zinszahlungen an und der "
"Saldo bleibt gleich."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator_uk.html:295
msgid ""
"Results may differ from lender quotes due to rounding and product-specific "
"rules."
msgstr ""
"Aufgrund von Rundungen und produktspezifischen Regeln können die Ergebnisse "
"von den Angeboten der Kreditgeber abweichen."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator_uk.html:421
msgid "Expected payoff"
msgstr "Erwartete Auszahlung"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator_uk.html:435
msgid "No schedule available for this mortgage type."
msgstr "Für diese Hypothekenart ist kein Zeitplan verfügbar."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:5
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:14
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:22
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:67
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:75
msgid "Mortgage Payoff Calculator"
msgstr "Hypothekenrückzahlungsrechner"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:5
msgid "Calculate Payoff Date & Savings"
msgstr "Berechnen Sie den Auszahlungstermin und die Ersparnisse"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:7
msgid ""
"Free mortgage payoff calculator to find when your mortgage will be paid off."
" See how extra payments, biweekly payments, or lump sums can save you money."
msgstr ""
"Kostenloser Hypothekentilgungsrechner, um herauszufinden, wann Ihre Hypothek"
" getilgt wird. Erfahren Sie, wie Sie durch zusätzliche Zahlungen, "
"zweiwöchentliche Zahlungen oder Pauschalbeträge Geld sparen können."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:10
msgid ""
"mortgage payoff calculator, early mortgage payoff, extra payment calculator,"
" biweekly payment savings, mortgage interest savings"
msgstr ""
"Hypothekenrückzahlungsrechner, vorzeitige Hypothekenrückzahlung, "
"Zusatzzahlungsrechner, zweiwöchentliche Zahlungsersparnisse, "
"Hypothekenzinsersparnisse"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:15
msgid ""
"Calculate when your mortgage will be paid off and see how extra payments "
"save money."
msgstr ""
"Berechnen Sie, wann Ihre Hypothek abbezahlt wird, und sehen Sie, wie "
"zusätzliche Zahlungen Geld sparen."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:23
msgid "Calculate mortgage payoff date and savings with extra payments"
msgstr ""
"Berechnen Sie das Tilgungsdatum der Hypothek und die Ersparnisse mit "
"zusätzlichen Zahlungen"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:38
msgid "How do extra payments save money?"
msgstr "Wie sparen zusätzliche Zahlungen Geld?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:41
msgid ""
"Extra payments go directly to principal, reducing the balance that accrues "
"interest. This means you pay less interest overall and finish your loan "
"faster."
msgstr ""
"Zusätzliche Zahlungen gehen direkt an den Kapitalbetrag und verringern so "
"den Saldo, für den Zinsen anfallen. Dadurch zahlen Sie insgesamt weniger "
"Zinsen und können Ihren Kredit schneller abwickeln."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:46
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:507
msgid "What are biweekly payments?"
msgstr "Was sind zweiwöchentliche Zahlungen?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:49
msgid ""
"Biweekly payments mean paying half your monthly payment every two weeks. "
"With 52 weeks per year, you make 26 half-payments (13 full payments) instead"
" of 12."
msgstr ""
"Zweiwöchentliche Zahlungen bedeuten, dass Sie alle zwei Wochen die Hälfte "
"Ihrer monatlichen Zahlung zahlen. Bei 52 Wochen im Jahr leisten Sie statt 12"
" 26 halbe Raten (13 volle Raten)."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:76
msgid ""
"Calculate how extra payments or biweekly payments can save on interest and "
"shorten your mortgage term."
msgstr ""
"Berechnen Sie, wie zusätzliche Zahlungen oder zweiwöchentliche Zahlungen "
"Zinsen sparen und die Laufzeit Ihrer Hypothek verkürzen können."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:87
