#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:491
#, python-format
msgid ""
"A one-time $1,000 payment on a $200,000 loan at 5%% can save $3,420 in "
"interest and pay off 4 months early."
msgstr ""
"Eine einmalige Zahlung von 1.000 $ für ein Darlehen von 200.000 $ zu 5 % "
"kann 3.420 $ an Zinsen einsparen und vier Monate früher zurückzahlen."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:508
msgid ""
"Pay half your mortgage every two weeks. With 52 weeks/year, you make 26 "
"half-payments (13 full payments) instead of 12, paying off faster."
msgstr ""
"Zahlen Sie alle zwei Wochen die Hälfte Ihrer Hypothek. Bei 52 Wochen/Jahr "
"leisten Sie 26 halbe Raten (13 volle Raten) statt 12 und amortisieren sich "
"schneller."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:511
msgid "Are there prepayment penalties?"
msgstr "Gibt es Vorfälligkeitsentschädigungen?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:512
msgid ""
"Some loans have penalties for paying off early. FHA, VA, and most federal "
"loans prohibit prepayment penalties. Check your loan documents."
msgstr ""
"Bei einigen Krediten fallen Strafen für die vorzeitige Rückzahlung an. FHA, "
"VA und die meisten Bundesdarlehen verbieten Vorfälligkeitsentschädigungen. "
"Überprüfen Sie Ihre Kreditunterlagen."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:515
msgid "Should I pay extra or invest instead?"
msgstr "Soll ich extra bezahlen oder stattdessen investieren?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:516
msgid ""
"It depends on your interest rate vs potential returns, tax situation, and "
"risk tolerance. Consider consulting a financial advisor."
