#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/gfr_calculator.html:318
msgid "Moderately to severely decreased kidney function"
msgstr "Mäßig bis stark eingeschränkte Nierenfunktion"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/gfr_calculator.html:323
msgid "Severely decreased kidney function"
msgstr "Stark verminderte Nierenfunktion"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/gfr_calculator.html:328
msgid "Kidney failure"
msgstr "Nierenversagen"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/gfr_calculator.html:349
msgid "What is GFR?"
msgstr "Was ist GFR?"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/gfr_calculator.html:351
msgid ""
"GFR (Glomerular Filtration Rate) is a measure of how well your kidneys are "
"filtering waste from your blood. It represents the rate at which fluid is "
"filtered through the glomeruli (tiny filters in the kidneys) per unit of "
"time."
msgstr ""
"Die GFR (glomeruläre Filtrationsrate) ist ein Maß dafür, wie gut Ihre Nieren"
" Abfallstoffe aus Ihrem Blut filtern. Sie stellt die Geschwindigkeit dar, "
"mit der Flüssigkeit pro Zeiteinheit durch die Glomeruli (winzige Filter in "
"den Nieren) gefiltert wird."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/gfr_calculator.html:354
msgid ""
"eGFR (estimated GFR) is calculated using formulas that take into account "
"your creatinine level, age, gender, and race. It's expressed in milliliters "
"per minute per 1.73 square meters of body surface area (mL/min/1.73m²)."
msgstr ""
"eGFR (geschätzte GFR) wird anhand von Formeln berechnet, die Ihren "
"Kreatininspiegel, Ihr Alter, Ihr Geschlecht und Ihre Rasse berücksichtigen. "
"Sie wird in Millilitern pro Minute pro 1,73 Quadratmeter Körperoberfläche "
"(ml/min/1,73 m²) ausgedrückt."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/gfr_calculator.html:360
msgid "Why GFR is Important"
msgstr "Warum GFR wichtig ist"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/gfr_calculator.html:362
msgid ""
"GFR is the best overall indicator of kidney function. It helps healthcare "
"providers:"
msgstr ""
"Die GFR ist der beste Gesamtindikator für die Nierenfunktion. Es hilft "
"Gesundheitsdienstleistern:"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/gfr_calculator.html:365
msgid "Detect kidney disease early"
msgstr "Nierenerkrankungen frühzeitig erkennen"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/gfr_calculator.html:366
msgid "Monitor kidney function over time"
msgstr "Überwachen Sie die Nierenfunktion im Laufe der Zeit"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/gfr_calculator.html:367
msgid "Determine the stage of chronic kidney disease (CKD)"
msgstr "Bestimmen Sie das Stadium einer chronischen Nierenerkrankung (CKD)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/gfr_calculator.html:368
msgid "Make decisions about treatment and medication dosing"
msgstr ""
"Treffen Sie Entscheidungen über die Behandlung und Medikamentendosierung"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/gfr_calculator.html:369
msgid "Assess the risk of kidney disease progression"
msgstr "Bewerten Sie das Risiko eines Fortschreitens der Nierenerkrankung"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/gfr_calculator.html:377
msgid "Enter your age (18-100 years)"
msgstr "Geben Sie Ihr Alter ein (18-100 Jahre)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/gfr_calculator.html:378
msgid "Select your gender (male or female)"
msgstr "Wählen Sie Ihr Geschlecht (männlich oder weiblich)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/gfr_calculator.html:379
msgid "Select your race (used for formula adjustment)"
msgstr "Wählen Sie Ihre Rasse aus (wird zur Formelanpassung verwendet)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/gfr_calculator.html:380
msgid "Choose your creatinine unit (mg/dL or μmol/L)"
msgstr "Wählen Sie Ihre Kreatinin-Einheit (mg/dL oder μmol/L)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/gfr_calculator.html:381
msgid "Enter your serum creatinine level from your blood test"
msgstr "Geben Sie Ihren Serumkreatininspiegel aus Ihrem Bluttest ein"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/gfr_calculator.html:382
msgid "Click 'Calculate eGFR' to see your results"
msgstr "Klicken Sie auf „eGFR berechnen“, um Ihre Ergebnisse anzuzeigen"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/gfr_calculator.html:383
msgid "Review your eGFR value, CKD stage, and kidney function assessment"
msgstr ""
"Überprüfen Sie Ihren eGFR-Wert, das CKD-Stadium und die Beurteilung der "
"Nierenfunktion"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/gfr_calculator.html:392
msgid "eGFR Value"
msgstr "eGFR-Wert"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/gfr_calculator.html:394
msgid ""
"Your estimated glomerular filtration rate in mL/min/1.73m². Higher values "
"indicate better kidney function. Normal eGFR is typically 90 or higher."
msgstr ""
"Ihre geschätzte glomeruläre Filtrationsrate in ml/min/1,73 m². Höhere Werte "
"weisen auf eine bessere Nierenfunktion hin. Die normale eGFR liegt "
"typischerweise bei 90 oder höher."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/gfr_calculator.html:398
msgid "CKD Stage"
msgstr "CKD-Stadium"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/gfr_calculator.html:400
msgid ""
"Your chronic kidney disease stage based on your eGFR value. Stages range "
"from Stage 1 (normal/high) to Stage 5 (kidney failure)."
msgstr ""
"Ihr chronisches Nierenerkrankungsstadium basierend auf Ihrem eGFR-Wert. Die "
"Stadien reichen von Stadium 1 (normal/hoch) bis Stadium 5 (Nierenversagen)."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/gfr_calculator.html:404
msgid "CKD-EPI vs MDRD"
msgstr "CKD-EPI vs. MDRD"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/gfr_calculator.html:406
msgid ""
"The calculator shows results from both formulas. CKD-EPI is the preferred "
"formula as it's more accurate, especially at higher eGFR levels. MDRD is "
"shown for comparison."
msgstr ""
"Der Rechner zeigt Ergebnisse beider Formeln an. CKD-EPI ist die bevorzugte "
"Formel, da sie genauer ist, insbesondere bei höheren eGFR-Werten. Zum "
"Vergleich ist MDRD dargestellt."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/gfr_calculator.html:414
msgid "Chronic Kidney Disease Stages Explained"
msgstr "Erklärte Stadien chronischer Nierenerkrankungen"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/gfr_calculator.html:417
msgid "Stage 1 (eGFR ≥ 90)"
msgstr "Stufe 1 (eGFR ≥ 90)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/gfr_calculator.html:419
msgid ""
"Normal or high kidney function. May have kidney damage but function is "
"preserved. Regular monitoring recommended."
msgstr ""
"Normale oder hohe Nierenfunktion. Möglicherweise liegt eine Nierenschädigung"
" vor, die Funktion bleibt jedoch erhalten. Regelmäßige Überwachung "
"empfohlen."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/gfr_calculator.html:423
msgid "Stage 2 (eGFR 60-89)"
msgstr "Stufe 2 (eGFR 60-89)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/gfr_calculator.html:425
msgid ""
"Mildly decreased kidney function. Kidney damage with mild loss of function. "
"Monitoring and lifestyle changes recommended."
msgstr ""
"Leicht verminderte Nierenfunktion. Nierenschaden mit leichtem "
"Funktionsverlust. Überwachung und Änderungen des Lebensstils werden "
"empfohlen."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/gfr_calculator.html:429
msgid "Stage 3a (eGFR 45-59)"
msgstr "Stufe 3a (eGFR 45-59)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/gfr_calculator.html:431
msgid ""
"Mildly to moderately decreased kidney function. More frequent monitoring and"
" may need to see a nephrologist."
msgstr ""
"Leicht bis mäßig eingeschränkte Nierenfunktion. Häufigere Überwachung und "
"möglicherweise die Notwendigkeit, einen Nephrologen aufzusuchen."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/gfr_calculator.html:435
msgid "Stage 3b (eGFR 30-44)"
msgstr "Stufe 3b (eGFR 30-44)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/gfr_calculator.html:437
msgid ""
"Moderately to severely decreased kidney function. Regular nephrologist "
"visits and treatment planning recommended."
msgstr ""
"Mäßig bis stark verminderte Nierenfunktion. Regelmäßige Besuche beim "
"Nephrologen und Behandlungsplanung werden empfohlen."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/gfr_calculator.html:441
msgid "Stage 4 (eGFR 15-29)"
msgstr "Stufe 4 (eGFR 15–29)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/gfr_calculator.html:443
msgid ""
"Severely decreased kidney function. Preparation for kidney replacement "
"therapy (dialysis or transplant) should begin."
msgstr ""
"Stark verminderte Nierenfunktion. Die Vorbereitung auf eine "
"Nierenersatztherapie (Dialyse oder Transplantation) sollte beginnen."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/gfr_calculator.html:447
msgid "Stage 5 (eGFR < 15)"
msgstr "Stufe 5 (eGFR < 15)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/gfr_calculator.html:449
msgid ""
"Kidney failure. Dialysis or kidney transplant is typically needed. Also "
"called end-stage renal disease (ESRD)."
msgstr ""
"Nierenversagen. Typischerweise ist eine Dialyse oder eine "
"Nierentransplantation erforderlich. Wird auch als terminale "
"Niereninsuffizienz (ESRD) bezeichnet."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/gfr_calculator.html:457
msgid "eGFR Formulas Explained"
msgstr "eGFR-Formeln erklärt"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/gfr_calculator.html:460
msgid "CKD-EPI Formula"
msgstr "CKD-EPI-Formel"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/gfr_calculator.html:462
msgid ""
"The preferred formula for calculating eGFR. More accurate than MDRD, "
"especially at higher eGFR levels (above 60). Recommended by most medical "
"organizations."
msgstr ""
"Die bevorzugte Formel zur Berechnung der eGFR. Genauer als MDRD, "
"insbesondere bei höheren eGFR-Werten (über 60). Von den meisten "
"medizinischen Organisationen empfohlen."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/gfr_calculator.html:464
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/gfr_calculator.html:471
msgid "Takes into account: Creatinine, age, gender, and race"
msgstr "Berücksichtigt: Kreatinin, Alter, Geschlecht und Rasse"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/gfr_calculator.html:467
msgid "MDRD Formula"
msgstr "MDRD-Formel"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/gfr_calculator.html:469
msgid ""
"An older formula still used for comparison. Less accurate at higher eGFR "
"levels but useful for historical comparison."
msgstr ""
"Zum Vergleich wird noch eine ältere Formel verwendet. Bei höheren eGFR-"
"Werten weniger genau, aber nützlich für historische Vergleiche."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/gfr_calculator.html:478
msgid "Factors Affecting GFR"
msgstr "Faktoren, die die GFR beeinflussen"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/gfr_calculator.html:480
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/healthy_weight_calculator.html:363
msgid "Age:"
msgstr "Alter:"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/gfr_calculator.html:480
msgid ""
"GFR naturally decreases with age. Normal decline is about 1 mL/min/1.73m² "
"per year after age 40."
msgstr ""
"Die GFR nimmt mit zunehmendem Alter natürlich ab. Der normale Rückgang "
"beträgt etwa 1 ml/min/1,73 m² pro Jahr nach dem 40. Lebensjahr."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/gfr_calculator.html:481
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/healthy_weight_calculator.html:364
msgid "Gender:"
msgstr "Geschlecht:"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/gfr_calculator.html:481
msgid ""
"Men typically have higher muscle mass and creatinine levels, which affects "
"the calculation."
msgstr ""
"Männer haben typischerweise eine höhere Muskelmasse und einen höheren "
"Kreatininspiegel, was sich auf die Berechnung auswirkt."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/gfr_calculator.html:482
msgid "Race:"
msgstr "Wettrennen:"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/gfr_calculator.html:482
msgid ""
"The formulas include race adjustments based on research showing differences "
"in muscle mass and creatinine production."
msgstr ""
"Die Formeln umfassen Rassenanpassungen, die auf Untersuchungen basieren, die"
" Unterschiede in der Muskelmasse und der Kreatininproduktion zeigen."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/gfr_calculator.html:483
msgid "Creatinine Level:"
msgstr "Kreatininspiegel:"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/gfr_calculator.html:483
msgid ""
"Higher creatinine levels indicate reduced kidney function, as kidneys are "
"less able to filter waste from the blood."
msgstr ""
"Höhere Kreatininwerte weisen auf eine verminderte Nierenfunktion hin, da die"
" Nieren weniger in der Lage sind, Abfallstoffe aus dem Blut zu filtern."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/gfr_calculator.html:484
msgid "Muscle Mass:"
msgstr "Muskelmasse:"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/gfr_calculator.html:484
msgid ""
"People with higher muscle mass produce more creatinine, which can affect "
"eGFR calculations."
msgstr ""
"Menschen mit größerer Muskelmasse produzieren mehr Kreatinin, was sich auf "
"die eGFR-Berechnungen auswirken kann."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/gfr_calculator.html:496
msgid ""
"eGFR is an estimate. Actual GFR can only be measured directly through "
"specialized tests. The calculator provides estimates based on standard "
"formulas."
msgstr ""
"eGFR ist eine Schätzung. Die tatsächliche GFR kann nur durch spezielle Tests"
" direkt gemessen werden. Der Rechner liefert Schätzungen basierend auf "
"Standardformeln."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/gfr_calculator.html:502
msgid ""
"eGFR may not be accurate for certain populations, including children, "
"pregnant women, people with very high or low muscle mass, or those with "
"rapidly changing kidney function."
msgstr ""
"Die eGFR ist für bestimmte Bevölkerungsgruppen möglicherweise nicht genau, "
"darunter Kinder, schwangere Frauen, Menschen mit sehr hoher oder geringer "
"Muskelmasse oder Menschen mit sich schnell ändernder Nierenfunktion."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/gfr_calculator.html:508
msgid ""
"A single eGFR measurement may not be diagnostic. Healthcare providers "
"typically look at trends over time and consider other factors like protein "
"in urine."
msgstr ""
"Eine einzelne eGFR-Messung ist möglicherweise nicht diagnostisch. "
"Gesundheitsdienstleister betrachten in der Regel Trends im Laufe der Zeit "
"und berücksichtigen andere Faktoren wie Protein im Urin."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/gfr_calculator.html:514
msgid ""
"This calculator is for educational and informational purposes only. Always "
"consult with healthcare providers for accurate kidney function assessment, "
"diagnosis, and treatment decisions."
msgstr ""
"Dieser Rechner dient nur zu Bildungs- und Informationszwecken. Wenden Sie "
"sich für eine genaue Beurteilung der Nierenfunktion, Diagnose und "
"Behandlungsentscheidungen immer an einen Arzt."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/gfr_calculator.html:733
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/gfr_calculator.html:839
msgid "mL/min/1.73m²"
msgstr "ml/min/1,73 m²"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/gfr_calculator.html:786
msgid "Your Stage"
msgstr "Deine Bühne"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/healthy_weight_calculator.html:4
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/healthy_weight_calculator.html:14
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/healthy_weight_calculator.html:23
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/healthy_weight_calculator.html:44
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/healthy_weight_calculator.html:56
msgid "Healthy Weight Calculator"
msgstr "Rechner für gesundes Gewicht"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/healthy_weight_calculator.html:4
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/healthy_weight_calculator.html:14
msgid "Calculate Healthy Weight Range"
msgstr "Berechnen Sie den gesunden Gewichtsbereich"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/healthy_weight_calculator.html:5
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/healthy_weight_calculator.html:15
msgid ""
"Calculate your healthy weight range based on BMI categories. Get ideal "
"weight recommendations for your height."
msgstr ""
"Berechnen Sie Ihren gesunden Gewichtsbereich basierend auf BMI-Kategorien. "
