msgid "Check protein recommendations based on your activity level"
msgstr ""
"Überprüfen Sie die Proteinempfehlungen basierend auf Ihrem Aktivitätsniveau"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/lean_body_mass_calculator.html:343
msgid "Lean Body Mass (LBM)"
msgstr "Magere Körpermasse (LBM)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/lean_body_mass_calculator.html:345
msgid ""
"Your total body weight minus all fat. This includes muscles, bones, organs, "
"and water. Higher LBM generally indicates better body composition."
msgstr ""
"Ihr gesamtes Körpergewicht abzüglich sämtlicher Fette. Dazu gehören Muskeln,"
" Knochen, Organe und Wasser. Higher LBM generally indicates better body "
"composition."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/lean_body_mass_calculator.html:351
msgid ""
"The total weight of fat in your body. Calculated as a percentage of your "
"total weight."
msgstr ""
"Das Gesamtgewicht an Fett in Ihrem Körper. Berechnet als Prozentsatz Ihres "
"Gesamtgewichts."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/lean_body_mass_calculator.html:355
msgid "LBM Percentage"
msgstr "LBM-Prozentsatz"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/lean_body_mass_calculator.html:357
msgid ""
"The percentage of your total weight that is lean body mass. Higher "
"percentages indicate better body composition."
msgstr ""
"Der Prozentsatz Ihres Gesamtgewichts, der aus fettfreier Körpermasse "
"besteht. Höhere Prozentsätze weisen auf eine bessere Körperzusammensetzung "
"hin."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/lean_body_mass_calculator.html:361
msgid "Protein Recommendations"
msgstr "Proteinempfehlungen"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/lean_body_mass_calculator.html:363
msgid ""
"Based on your LBM and activity level. Sedentary individuals need less "
"protein, while athletes and bodybuilders need more to support muscle "
"maintenance and growth."
msgstr ""
"Basierend auf Ihrem LBM und Aktivitätsniveau. Personen mit einer sitzenden "
"Tätigkeit benötigen weniger Protein, während Sportler und Bodybuilder mehr "
"Protein benötigen, um den Muskelerhalt und das Muskelwachstum zu "
"unterstützen."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/lean_body_mass_calculator.html:371
msgid "Body Composition Categories"
msgstr "Kategorien der Körperzusammensetzung"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/lean_body_mass_calculator.html:374
#, python-format
msgid "Essential Fat: &lt; 6%%"
msgstr "Essentielles Fett: &lt; 6%%"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/lean_body_mass_calculator.html:376
msgid ""
"The minimum amount of fat necessary for basic physical and physiological "
"health. Typically only seen in competitive bodybuilders."
msgstr ""
"Die für die grundlegende körperliche und physiologische Gesundheit "
"erforderliche Mindestmenge an Fett. Wird normalerweise nur bei Wettkampf-"
"Bodybuildern beobachtet."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/lean_body_mass_calculator.html:380
#, python-format
msgid "Athletic: 6-14%%"
msgstr "Sportlich: 6-14 %%"

