#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:303
msgid "O'Conner Formula"
msgstr "O'Conner-Formel"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:305
msgid "Conservative estimate. Good for beginners."
msgstr "Konservative Schätzung. Gut für Anfänger."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:308
msgid "Mayhew Formula"
msgstr "Mayhew-Formel"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:310
msgid "Exponential formula. Accurate across wide rep ranges."
msgstr "Exponentialformel. Präzise über große Wiederholungsbereiche hinweg."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:313
msgid "Wathan Formula"
msgstr "Wathan-Formel"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:315
msgid "Another exponential formula. Good alternative to Mayhew."
msgstr "Eine weitere Exponentialformel. Gute Alternative zu Mayhew."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:319
msgid ""
"The calculator uses the average of all formulas for the most accurate "
"estimate. Different formulas may give slightly different results, which is "
"why using multiple formulas and averaging provides the best estimate."
msgstr ""
"Für die genaueste Schätzung verwendet der Rechner den Durchschnitt aller "
"Formeln. Unterschiedliche Formeln können leicht unterschiedliche Ergebnisse "
"liefern, weshalb die Verwendung mehrerer Formeln und die Mittelung die beste"
" Schätzung liefert."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:327
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_weight_gain_calculator.html:398
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:450
msgid "Select your unit system (Metric or Imperial)"
msgstr "Wählen Sie Ihr Einheitensystem (metrisch oder imperial)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:328
msgid ""
"Enter the weight you successfully lifted (use a weight you can lift for the "
"specified reps with good form)"
msgstr ""
"Geben Sie das Gewicht ein, das Sie erfolgreich gehoben haben (verwenden Sie "
"ein Gewicht, das Sie mit guter Form für die angegebenen Wiederholungen heben"
" können)."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:329
msgid "Enter the number of reps you performed (1-30 reps)"
msgstr ""
"Geben Sie die Anzahl der Wiederholungen ein, die Sie ausgeführt haben (1–30 "
"Wiederholungen)."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:330
msgid "Click 'Calculate 1RM' to see your estimated one rep max"
msgstr ""
"Klicken Sie auf „1RM berechnen“, um Ihr geschätztes Maximalgewicht für eine "
"Wiederholung anzuzeigen"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:331
msgid "Review the training percentages and rep estimates for program design"
msgstr ""
"Überprüfen Sie die Trainingsprozentsätze und Wiederholungsschätzungen für "
"die Programmgestaltung"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:332
msgid "Use the results to plan your training intensities"
msgstr "Nutzen Sie die Ergebnisse, um Ihre Trainingsintensitäten zu planen"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:341
msgid "Estimated 1RM"
msgstr "Geschätzte 1RM"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:343
msgid ""
"The average of all formulas. This is your best estimate of your true one rep"
" max. Use this as your reference point for training."
msgstr ""
"Der Durchschnitt aller Formeln. Dies ist Ihre beste Schätzung Ihrer "
"tatsächlichen maximalen Wiederholungszahl. Nutzen Sie dies als Referenzpunkt"
" für Ihr Training."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:349
#, python-format
msgid ""
"The weight you should lift at different percentages of your 1RM. Common "
"training zones: 50-60%% (endurance), 70-80%% (hypertrophy), 85-95%% "
"(strength), 100%% (maximal strength)."
msgstr ""
"Das Gewicht, das Sie in unterschiedlichen Prozentsätzen Ihres 1RM heben "
"sollten. Gängige Trainingsbereiche: 50–60 % (Ausdauer), 70–80 % "
"(Hypertrophie), 85–95 % (Kraft), 100 % (Maximalkraft)."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:353
msgid "Estimated Max Reps"
msgstr "Geschätzte maximale Wiederholungen"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:355
msgid ""
"Approximate number of reps you could perform at different percentages of "
"your 1RM. Useful for rep-based training programs."
msgstr ""
"Ungefähre Anzahl an Wiederholungen, die Sie mit unterschiedlichen "
"Prozentsätzen Ihres 1RM ausführen könnten. Nützlich für rep-basierte "
"Trainingsprogramme."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:359
msgid "Formula Comparison"
msgstr "Formelvergleich"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:361
msgid ""
"Shows how different formulas estimate your 1RM. The range gives you an idea "
"of the uncertainty in the estimate."
msgstr ""
"Zeigt, wie verschiedene Formeln Ihr 1RM schätzen. Der Bereich gibt Ihnen "
"eine Vorstellung von der Unsicherheit der Schätzung."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:369
msgid "Training Zones by Percentage"
msgstr "Trainingszonen nach Prozentsatz"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:372
#, python-format
msgid "50-60%%: Endurance Zone"
msgstr "50–60 %: Ausdauerzone"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:374
msgid ""
"High volume, low intensity. Builds muscular endurance and work capacity. "
"12-20+ reps."
msgstr ""
"Hohe Lautstärke, geringe Intensität. Baut Muskelausdauer und "
"Arbeitskapazität auf. 12–20+ Wiederholungen."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:378
#, python-format
msgid "70-80%%: Hypertrophy Zone"
msgstr "70–80 %: Hypertrophiezone"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:380
msgid "Moderate volume and intensity. Optimal for muscle growth. 8-12 reps."
msgstr ""
"Mäßige Lautstärke und Intensität. Optimal für den Muskelaufbau. 8-12 "
"Wiederholungen."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:384
#, python-format
msgid "85-95%%: Strength Zone"
msgstr "85–95 %: Kraftzone"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:386
msgid "High intensity, lower volume. Builds maximal strength. 1-5 reps."
msgstr ""
"Hohe Intensität, geringere Lautstärke. Baut maximale Kraft auf. 1-5 "
"Wiederholungen."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:390
#, python-format
msgid "95-100%%: Maximal Strength"
msgstr "95–100 %: Maximale Stärke"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:392
msgid "Peak intensity. Used sparingly for testing or peaking. 1 rep only."
msgstr ""
"Spitzenintensität. Sparsam zum Testen oder Peaking verwendet. Nur 1 "
"Wiederholung."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:406
msgid ""
"1RM estimates are most accurate when using 1-10 reps. Accuracy decreases "
"with higher rep counts."
msgstr ""
"1RM-Schätzungen sind am genauesten, wenn 1–10 Wiederholungen verwendet "
"werden. Die Genauigkeit nimmt mit höherer Wiederholungszahl ab."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:412
msgid ""
"Always use a weight you can lift with proper form. Poor form leads to "
"inaccurate estimates and injury risk."
msgstr ""
"Verwenden Sie immer ein Gewicht, das Sie mit der richtigen Form heben "
"können. Eine schlechte Form führt zu ungenauen Schätzungen und einem "
"Verletzungsrisiko."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:418
msgid ""
"1RM varies by exercise. Bench press, squat, and deadlift will have different"
" 1RMs. Calculate separately for each."
msgstr ""
"1RM variiert je nach Übung. Bankdrücken, Kniebeugen und Kreuzheben haben "
"unterschiedliche 1RMs. Berechnen Sie jeweils separat."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:424
msgid ""
"If you want to test your true 1RM, do so with proper warm-up, spotters, and "
"safety equipment. Consider working with a qualified strength coach."
msgstr ""
"Wenn Sie Ihr wahres 1RM-Gewicht testen möchten, tun Sie dies mit dem "
"richtigen Aufwärmen, Spottern und Sicherheitsausrüstung. Erwägen Sie die "
"Zusammenarbeit mit einem qualifizierten Krafttrainer."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:5
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:14
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:23
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:48
msgid "Overweight Calculator"
msgstr "Übergewichtsrechner"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:5
msgid "BMI Assessment & Weight Analysis"
msgstr "BMI-Bewertung und Gewichtsanalyse"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:7
msgid ""
"Calculate BMI and determine if you are overweight. Get detailed assessment, "
"ideal weight range, and recommendations for healthy weight management."
msgstr ""
"Berechnen Sie den BMI und stellen Sie fest, ob Sie übergewichtig sind. "
"Erhalten Sie eine detaillierte Einschätzung, den idealen Gewichtsbereich und"
" Empfehlungen für ein gesundes Gewichtsmanagement."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:10
msgid ""
"overweight calculator, BMI calculator, weight assessment, obesity "
"calculator, healthy weight"
msgstr ""
"Übergewichtsrechner, BMI-Rechner, Gewichtsbewertung, Fettleibigkeitsrechner,"
" gesundes Gewicht"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:14
msgid "BMI Assessment"
msgstr "BMI-Bewertung"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:15
msgid "Calculate BMI and determine if you are overweight."
msgstr ""
"Berechnen Sie den BMI und stellen Sie fest, ob Sie übergewichtig sind."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:24
msgid "Calculate BMI and determine if overweight"
msgstr "Berechnen Sie den BMI und stellen Sie fest, ob Sie übergewichtig sind"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:51
msgid ""
"Calculate your BMI and determine if you are overweight. Get detailed "
"assessment, ideal weight range, and personalized recommendations for healthy"
" weight management."
msgstr ""
"Berechnen Sie Ihren BMI und stellen Sie fest, ob Sie übergewichtig sind. "
"Erhalten Sie eine detaillierte Beurteilung, den idealen Gewichtsbereich und "
"personalisierte Empfehlungen für ein gesundes Gewichtsmanagement."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:94
msgid "Range: 50-300 cm"
msgstr "Reichweite: 50–300 cm"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:171
msgid ""
"Enter your height and weight, then click Calculate to see your BMI "
"assessment with detailed analysis, ideal weight range, and recommendations."
msgstr ""
"Geben Sie Ihre Größe und Ihr Gewicht ein und klicken Sie dann auf Berechnen,"
" um Ihre BMI-Bewertung mit detaillierter Analyse, Idealgewichtsbereich und "
"Empfehlungen anzuzeigen."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:194
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_weight_gain_calculator.html:110
msgid "Current Weight"
msgstr "Aktuelles Gewicht"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:200
msgid "Ideal Range"
msgstr "Ideale Reichweite"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:206
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:624
msgid "Weight to Lose"
msgstr "Gewicht zu verlieren"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:247
msgid "Weight Comparison"
msgstr "Gewichtsvergleich"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:285
msgid "Assessment Details"
msgstr "Bewertungsdetails"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:306
msgid "What Does It Mean to Be Overweight?"
msgstr "Was bedeutet es, übergewichtig zu sein?"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:308
msgid ""
"Being overweight means having a Body Mass Index (BMI) of 25 or higher. BMI "
"is calculated using your weight and height to estimate body fat. While BMI "
"is a useful screening tool, it doesn't directly measure body fat or account "
"for muscle mass."
msgstr ""
"Übergewicht bedeutet, einen Body-Mass-Index (BMI) von 25 oder höher zu "
"haben. Der BMI wird anhand Ihres Gewichts und Ihrer Größe berechnet, um den "
"Körperfettanteil abzuschätzen. Obwohl der BMI ein nützliches Screening-"
"Instrument ist, misst er weder direkt den Körperfettanteil noch "
"berücksichtigt er die Muskelmasse."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:314
msgid ""
"BMI categories: Underweight (<18.5), Normal Weight (18.5-24.9), Overweight "
"(25-29.9), Obese (≥30). Being overweight or obese increases the risk of "
"various health conditions."
msgstr ""
"BMI-Kategorien: Untergewicht (<18,5), Normalgewicht (18,5–24,9), Übergewicht"
" (25–29,9), Fettleibig (≥30). Übergewicht oder Fettleibigkeit erhöhen das "
"Risiko für verschiedene Gesundheitszustände."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:323
msgid "Underweight: BMI &lt; 18.5"
msgstr "Untergewicht: BMI &lt; 18.5"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:325
msgid ""
"Includes severe thinness (<16), moderate thinness (16-17), and mild thinness"
" (17-18.5). May need to gain weight. Consult with a healthcare provider."
msgstr ""
"Umfasst starke Schlankheit (<16), mäßige Schlankheit (16–17) und leichte "
"Schlankheit (17–18,5). Möglicherweise muss man zunehmen. Konsultieren Sie "
"einen Gesundheitsdienstleister."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:329
msgid "Normal Weight: BMI 18.5-24.9"
msgstr "Normalgewicht: BMI 18,5-24,9"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:331
msgid ""
"Healthy weight range. Continue maintaining a balanced diet and regular "
"physical activity."
msgstr ""
"Gesunder Gewichtsbereich. Achten Sie weiterhin auf eine ausgewogene "
"Ernährung und regelmäßige körperliche Aktivität."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:335
msgid "Overweight: BMI 25-29.9"
msgstr "Übergewicht: BMI 25-29,9"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:337
msgid ""
"Above healthy weight range. Consider a balanced diet and regular exercise to"
" reach a healthy weight."
msgstr ""
"Oberhalb des gesunden Gewichtsbereichs. Denken Sie an eine ausgewogene "
"Ernährung und regelmäßige Bewegung, um ein gesundes Gewicht zu erreichen."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:341
msgid "Obese: BMI ≥ 30"
msgstr "Fettleibig: BMI ≥ 30"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:343
msgid ""
"Includes Obese Class I (30-35), Class II (35-40), and Class III (>40). "
"Consult with healthcare professionals for a comprehensive weight management "
"plan."
msgstr ""
"Umfasst Fettleibigkeit der Klassen I (30–35), Klasse II (35–40) und Klasse "
"III (>40). Konsultieren Sie medizinisches Fachpersonal für einen umfassenden"
" Plan zur Gewichtskontrolle."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:356
msgid "Click 'Calculate BMI' to see your assessment"
msgstr "Klicken Sie auf „BMI berechnen“, um Ihre Einschätzung anzuzeigen"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:357
msgid "Review your BMI, category, and ideal weight range"
msgstr ""
"Überprüfen Sie Ihren BMI, Ihre Kategorie und Ihren idealen Gewichtsbereich"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:358
msgid "Check the weight you need to lose or gain to reach healthy range"
msgstr ""
"Überprüfen Sie das Gewicht, das Sie verlieren oder zunehmen müssen, um einen"
" gesunden Bereich zu erreichen"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:359
msgid "Read the comprehensive guide for interpretation and recommendations"
msgstr ""
"Lesen Sie den umfassenden Leitfaden für Interpretationen und Empfehlungen"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:370
msgid ""
"Your calculated Body Mass Index. This number is used to categorize your "
"weight status."
msgstr ""
"Ihr berechneter Body-Mass-Index. Diese Nummer wird zur Kategorisierung Ihres"
" Gewichtsstatus verwendet."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:376
msgid ""
"Your weight status based on WHO BMI classification. Categories range from "
"Underweight to Obese Class III."
msgstr ""
"Ihr Gewichtsstatus basierend auf der BMI-Klassifizierung der WHO. Die "
"Kategorien reichen von Untergewicht bis Fettleibigkeit der Klasse III."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:382
msgid ""
"The weight range (BMI 18.5-24.9) considered healthy for your height. This is"
" your target range for optimal health."
msgstr ""
"Der Gewichtsbereich (BMI 18,5–24,9) gilt als gesund für Ihre Körpergröße. "
"Dies ist Ihr Zielbereich für eine optimale Gesundheit."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:386
msgid "Weight to Lose/Gain"
msgstr "Gewicht zu verlieren/zunehmen"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:388
msgid ""
"The amount of weight you need to lose (if overweight) or gain (if "
"underweight) to reach the healthy weight range."
msgstr ""
"Die Menge an Gewicht, die Sie verlieren (bei Übergewicht) oder zunehmen (bei"
" Untergewicht) müssen, um den gesunden Gewichtsbereich zu erreichen."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:396
msgid "Health Risks of Being Overweight"
msgstr "Gesundheitsrisiken von Übergewicht"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:398
msgid "Being overweight or obese increases the risk of:"
msgstr "Übergewicht oder Fettleibigkeit erhöhen das Risiko für:"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:400
msgid "Type 2 diabetes"
msgstr "Typ-2-Diabetes"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:401
msgid "High blood pressure and heart disease"
msgstr "Hoher Blutdruck und Herzerkrankungen"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:402
msgid "Stroke"
msgstr "Schlaganfall"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:403
msgid "Certain types of cancer"
msgstr "Bestimmte Krebsarten"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:404
msgid "Sleep apnea"
msgstr "Schlafapnoe"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:405
msgid "Osteoarthritis"
msgstr "Arthrose"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:406
msgid "Fatty liver disease"
msgstr "Fettlebererkrankung"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:407
msgid "Kidney disease"
msgstr "Nierenerkrankung"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:417
msgid "Balanced Diet"
msgstr "Ausgewogene Ernährung"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:419
msgid ""
"Focus on whole foods, fruits, vegetables, lean proteins, and whole grains. "
"Control portion sizes and reduce processed foods."
msgstr ""
"Konzentrieren Sie sich auf Vollwertkost, Obst, Gemüse, mageres Eiweiß und "
"Vollkornprodukte. Kontrollieren Sie die Portionsgrößen und reduzieren Sie "
"verarbeitete Lebensmittel."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:423
msgid "Regular Exercise"
msgstr "Regelmäßige Bewegung"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:425
msgid ""
"Aim for at least 150 minutes of moderate-intensity exercise per week. "
"Include both cardio and strength training."
msgstr ""
"Streben Sie mindestens 150 Minuten mäßig intensives Training pro Woche an. "
"Integrieren Sie sowohl Cardio- als auch Krafttraining."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:429
msgid "Lifestyle Changes"
msgstr "Änderungen des Lebensstils"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:431
msgid ""
"Get adequate sleep, manage stress, stay hydrated, and make sustainable "
"changes rather than quick fixes."
msgstr ""
"Sorgen Sie für ausreichend Schlaf, gehen Sie mit Stress um, bleiben Sie "
"hydriert und nehmen Sie nachhaltige Veränderungen statt schnelle Lösungen "
"vor."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:445
msgid ""
"BMI is a screening tool, not a diagnostic measure. It doesn't account for "
"muscle mass, bone density, or body composition."
msgstr ""
"Der BMI ist ein Screening-Instrument, kein diagnostisches Maß. Muskelmasse, "
"Knochendichte oder Körperzusammensetzung werden dabei nicht berücksichtigt."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:451
msgid ""
"Athletes or individuals with high muscle mass may have higher BMIs that "
"don't reflect excess fat."
msgstr ""
"Sportler oder Personen mit hoher Muskelmasse haben möglicherweise einen "
"höheren BMI, der nicht auf überschüssiges Fett zurückzuführen ist."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:457
msgid ""
"Weight loss should be gradual (0.5-1 kg or 1-2 lbs per week) for sustainable"
" results and health."
msgstr ""
"Für nachhaltige Ergebnisse und Gesundheit sollte der Gewichtsverlust "
"schrittweise erfolgen (0,5–1 kg pro Woche)."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:463
msgid ""
"If you're concerned about your weight or BMI, please consult with qualified "
"healthcare professionals or registered dietitians for personalized advice."
msgstr ""
"Wenn Sie sich Sorgen über Ihr Gewicht oder Ihren BMI machen, wenden Sie sich"
" bitte an qualifiziertes medizinisches Fachpersonal oder registrierte "
"Ernährungsberater, um eine persönliche Beratung zu erhalten."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:633
msgid "Healthy"
msgstr "Gesund"

