#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:260
msgid "What is Ovulation?"
msgstr "Was ist Eisprung?"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:262
msgid ""
"Ovulation is the process in which a mature egg is released from one of the "
"ovaries. This typically occurs once per menstrual cycle, approximately 14 "
"days before the start of your next period. The egg travels down the "
"fallopian tube where it can be fertilized by sperm."
msgstr ""
"Der Eisprung ist der Vorgang, bei dem eine reife Eizelle aus einem der "
"Eierstöcke freigesetzt wird. Dies geschieht normalerweise einmal pro "
"Menstruationszyklus, etwa 14 Tage vor Beginn Ihrer nächsten Periode. Die "
"Eizelle wandert durch den Eileiter, wo sie von Spermien befruchtet werden "
"kann."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:265
msgid ""
"Understanding when you ovulate is crucial for both conception planning and "
"natural family planning. The fertile window includes the days leading up to "
"and including ovulation, when conception is most likely to occur."
msgstr ""
"Das Verständnis des Zeitpunkts Ihres Eisprungs ist sowohl für die "
"Empfängnisplanung als auch für die natürliche Familienplanung von "
"entscheidender Bedeutung. Das fruchtbare Fenster umfasst die Tage vor und "
"einschließlich des Eisprungs, an denen eine Empfängnis am wahrscheinlichsten"
" ist."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:271
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:301
msgid "Menstrual Cycle Phases"
msgstr "Phasen des Menstruationszyklus"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:274
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:304
msgid "Menstruation (Days 1-5)"
msgstr "Menstruation (Tage 1-5)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:276
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:306
msgid ""
"The uterine lining is shed. This marks day 1 of your cycle. Typically lasts "
"3-7 days."
msgstr ""
"Die Gebärmutterschleimhaut wird abgestoßen. Dies markiert den ersten Tag "
"Ihres Zyklus. Dauert in der Regel 3-7 Tage."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:280
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:310
msgid "Follicular Phase (Days 1-13)"
msgstr "Follikelphase (Tage 1–13)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:282
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:312
msgid ""
"Follicles in the ovaries begin to mature. Estrogen levels rise, preparing "
"the uterine lining for potential pregnancy."
msgstr ""
"Follikel in den Eierstöcken beginnen zu reifen. Der Östrogenspiegel steigt "
"und bereitet die Gebärmutterschleimhaut auf eine mögliche Schwangerschaft "
"vor."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:286
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:316
msgid "Ovulation (Day 14, approximately)"
msgstr "Eisprung (ungefähr Tag 14)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:288
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:318
msgid ""
"A mature egg is released from the ovary. This is your most fertile day. The "
"egg survives for 12-24 hours after release."
msgstr ""
"Aus dem Eierstock wird eine reife Eizelle freigesetzt. Dies ist Ihr "
"fruchtbarster Tag. Das Ei überlebt nach der Freisetzung 12–24 Stunden."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:292
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:322
msgid "Fertile Window (5 days before + ovulation + 1 day after)"
msgstr "Fruchtbares Fenster (5 Tage vor + Eisprung + 1 Tag danach)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:294
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:324
msgid ""
"The best time for conception. Sperm can survive up to 5 days in the female "
"reproductive tract, so having intercourse in the days leading up to "
"ovulation increases chances of conception."
msgstr ""
"Die beste Zeit für die Empfängnis. Spermien können bis zu 5 Tage im "
"weiblichen Fortpflanzungstrakt überleben, sodass Geschlechtsverkehr in den "
"Tagen vor dem Eisprung die Wahrscheinlichkeit einer Empfängnis erhöht."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:298
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:328
msgid "Luteal Phase (Days 15-28)"
msgstr "Lutealphase (Tage 15–28)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:300
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:330
msgid ""
"After ovulation, the corpus luteum produces progesterone. If pregnancy "
"doesn't occur, hormone levels drop and menstruation begins."
msgstr ""
"Nach dem Eisprung produziert der Gelbkörper Progesteron. Kommt es nicht zu "
"einer Schwangerschaft, sinkt der Hormonspiegel und die Menstruation beginnt."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:310
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:340
msgid ""
"Enter the first day of your last menstrual period (the day bleeding started)"
msgstr ""
"Geben Sie den ersten Tag Ihrer letzten Menstruation ein (den Tag, an dem die"
" Blutung begann)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:311
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:341
msgid ""
"Enter your average cycle length (number of days from day 1 of one period to "
"day 1 of the next)"
msgstr ""
"Geben Sie Ihre durchschnittliche Zykluslänge ein (Anzahl der Tage vom ersten"
" Tag einer Periode bis zum ersten Tag der nächsten)."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:312
msgid "Click 'Calculate Ovulation' to see your predicted ovulation date"
msgstr ""
"Klicken Sie auf „Eisprung berechnen“, um den voraussichtlichen "
"Eisprungtermin anzuzeigen"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:313
msgid "Review your fertile window (the best days for conception)"
msgstr ""
"Überprüfen Sie Ihr fruchtbares Fenster (die besten Tage für die Empfängnis)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:314
msgid "Check the cycle timeline to see all phases of your cycle"
msgstr ""
"Sehen Sie sich die Zykluszeitleiste an, um alle Phasen Ihres Zyklus zu sehen"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:315
msgid ""
"Use the fertility probability chart to understand your peak fertility days"
msgstr ""
"Verwenden Sie die Fruchtbarkeitswahrscheinlichkeitstabelle, um Ihre Tage mit"
" der höchsten Fruchtbarkeit zu verstehen"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:324
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:206
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:360
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:237
msgid "Ovulation Date"
msgstr "Datum des Eisprungs"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:326
msgid ""
"The predicted day when ovulation occurs. This is calculated as 14 days "
"before your next expected period. This is your most fertile day."
msgstr ""
"Der vorhergesagte Tag, an dem der Eisprung stattfindet. Dies wird als 14 "
"Tage vor Ihrer nächsten erwarteten Periode berechnet. Dies ist Ihr "
"fruchtbarster Tag."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:332
msgid ""
"The 6-7 day period when conception is most likely. This includes 5 days "
"before ovulation, the day of ovulation, and 1 day after. Sperm can survive "
"up to 5 days, so having intercourse during this window maximizes chances of "
"conception."
msgstr ""
"Der Zeitraum von 6 bis 7 Tagen, in dem eine Empfängnis am wahrscheinlichsten"
" ist. Dazu gehören 5 Tage vor dem Eisprung, der Tag des Eisprungs und 1 Tag "
"danach. Spermien können bis zu 5 Tage überleben, sodass der "
"Geschlechtsverkehr in diesem Zeitfenster die Chancen auf eine Empfängnis "
"maximiert."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:338
msgid ""
"A visual representation of your entire cycle showing all phases: "
"menstruation, follicular, fertile window, ovulation, and luteal phase."
msgstr ""
"Eine visuelle Darstellung Ihres gesamten Zyklus mit allen Phasen: "
"Menstruation, Follikelphase, fruchtbares Fenster, Eisprung und Lutealphase."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:344
msgid ""
"Shows the estimated probability of conception on each day of your cycle. "
"Peak fertility occurs on ovulation day and the days immediately before it."
msgstr ""
"Zeigt die geschätzte Wahrscheinlichkeit einer Empfängnis an jedem Tag Ihres "
"Zyklus an. Die höchste Fruchtbarkeit erreicht man am Tag des Eisprungs und "
"an den Tagen unmittelbar davor."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:352
msgid "Signs of Ovulation"
msgstr "Anzeichen eines Eisprungs"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:354
msgid "Common signs that ovulation may be occurring:"
msgstr "Häufige Anzeichen dafür, dass ein Eisprung stattfinden könnte:"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:356
msgid "Change in cervical mucus (becomes clear, stretchy, like egg white)"
msgstr "Veränderung des Zervixschleims (wird klar, dehnbar, wie Eiweiß)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:357
msgid "Slight increase in basal body temperature"
msgstr "Leichter Anstieg der Basaltemperatur"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:358
msgid "Mild pelvic or abdominal pain (mittelschmerz)"
msgstr "Mild pelvic or abdominal pain (mittelschmerz)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:359
msgid "Increased libido"
msgstr "Erhöhte Libido"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:360
msgid "Positive ovulation predictor kit (OPK) result"
msgstr "Positives Ergebnis des Ovulation Predictor Kit (OPK)."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:373
msgid ""
"Ovulation calculators provide estimates based on average cycle patterns. "
"Actual ovulation timing can vary due to stress, illness, travel, or hormonal"
" changes."
msgstr ""
"Eisprungrechner liefern Schätzungen basierend auf durchschnittlichen "
"Zyklusmustern. Der tatsächliche Zeitpunkt des Eisprungs kann aufgrund von "
"Stress, Krankheit, Reisen oder hormonellen Veränderungen variieren."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:379
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:419
msgid ""
"For more accurate tracking, combine calendar method with other methods like "
"basal body temperature (BBT) charting, cervical mucus monitoring, or "
"ovulation predictor kits."
msgstr ""
"Für eine genauere Verfolgung kombinieren Sie die Kalendermethode mit anderen"
" Methoden wie der Darstellung der Basaltemperatur (BBT), der Überwachung des"
" Zervixschleims oder Kits zur Vorhersage des Eisprungs."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:385
msgid ""
"If you have irregular cycles, PCOS, or other reproductive health concerns, "
"consult with a healthcare provider or fertility specialist for personalized "
"guidance."
msgstr ""
"Wenn Sie unregelmäßige Zyklen, PCOS oder andere reproduktive "
"Gesundheitsprobleme haben, wenden Sie sich für eine individuelle Beratung an"
" einen Arzt oder Fruchtbarkeitsspezialisten."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:391
msgid ""
"This calculator is for informational purposes only and should not replace "
"professional medical advice. Always consult healthcare providers for "
"fertility planning and reproductive health concerns."
msgstr ""
"Dieser Rechner dient nur zu Informationszwecken und ersetzt nicht den "
"professionellen medizinischen Rat. Wenden Sie sich bei Fragen zur "
"Fruchtbarkeitsplanung und reproduktiven Gesundheit stets an einen Arzt."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:516
