msgstr ""
"Sehr aktiver Lebensstil. Körperliche Arbeit, tägliches intensives Training "
"oder mehrere Trainingseinheiten."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:419
