msgstr ""
"Der Rechner führt automatisch Einheitenumrechnungen zwischen Millionen, "
"Milliarden und Billionen durch."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gdp_calculator.html:432
msgid ""
"Expenditure and income approaches should yield the same GDP value in theory."
msgstr ""
